♪Standing here♪

14
00:00:48,030 --> 00:00:49,760
♪I set the rules that shackle me♪

15
00:00:50,130 --> 00:00:51,120
♪Learn to cure♪

16
00:00:51,380 --> 00:00:53,230
♪Eradicating the diseases of this land♪

17
00:00:53,490 --> 00:00:54,560
♪I am just a common man♪

18
00:00:54,560 --> 00:00:56,610
♪I wanted to take things step by step♪

19
00:00:56,790 --> 00:00:57,910
♪I am just a common man♪

20
00:00:57,910 --> 00:00:59,920
♪Never want to be a confused fool♪

21
00:01:00,170 --> 00:01:01,280
♪I am just a common man♪

22
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:02,960
♪Listening to the songs without dispute♪

23
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:04,580
♪Yet I always see the lonely souls♪

24
00:01:04,580 --> 00:01:06,800
♪But I always rush ahead♪

25
00:01:07,580 --> 00:01:10,690
♪Leaving my scribbles behind
for future generations to study♪

26
00:01:11,730 --> 00:01:14,240
♪The light that these hands cannot hide♪

27
00:01:14,240 --> 00:01:17,410
♪The justice gavel strikes
and releases countless burdens♪

28
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:20,760
♪Looking back, it's the same old story♪

29
00:01:21,080 --> 00:01:24,150
♪Time and space brought me
to another yellowed page♪

30
00:01:25,470 --> 00:01:26,830
♪Sunlight pierces through♪

31
00:01:26,830 --> 00:01:28,560
♪One comes and goes as one pleases♪

32
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:30,140
♪My Go board holds both sides♪

33
00:01:30,140 --> 00:01:31,870
♪When I set the game, learn to see♪

34
00:01:31,870 --> 00:01:33,530
♪Don't be a sore loser♪

35
00:01:33,530 --> 00:01:35,010
♪So many lies and deceits♪

36
00:01:35,010 --> 00:01:36,890
♪I can see through every play♪

37
00:01:36,890 --> 00:01:38,440
♪May I live and die
with the sun♪

38
00:01:38,620 --> 00:01:41,180
=Guardians of the Dafeng=

39
00:01:41,340 --> 00:01:44,140
=Episode 25=

40
00:04:28,700 --> 00:04:29,550
You...

41
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:31,030
Who are you?

42
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,390
Who am I?

43
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:41,520
I've seen you before.

44
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:44,030
Are you the demonic hand
at the Sangbo lakebed?

45
00:04:46,080 --> 00:04:48,000
I am called Shen Shu.

46
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:49,710
I wish to borrow your body

47
00:04:49,710 --> 00:04:50,790
to nourish my severed arm.

48
00:04:51,520 --> 00:04:52,760
I hope you can understand.

49
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:55,760
Why were you at the Sangbo lakebed?

50
00:04:56,150 --> 00:04:57,710
Sangbo Lake?

51
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:04,080
Why was I sealed in Sangbo Lake?

52
00:05:04,790 --> 00:05:05,880
Where did I come from?

53
00:05:05,880 --> 00:05:07,030
Why am I here?

54
00:05:07,030 --> 00:05:08,350
Who am I?

55
00:05:08,350 --> 00:05:09,210
I can't remember.

56
00:05:09,210 --> 00:05:10,560
In Sangbo Lake.

57
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,440
At the lakebed.

58
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:13,200
Why was I at Sangbo?

59
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:16,230
Where did I come from?

60
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:21,270
I...

61
00:05:22,270 --> 00:05:23,470
I got off the point.

62
00:05:30,150 --> 00:05:31,880
My primordial spirit is incomplete.

63
00:05:32,230 --> 00:05:34,270
So, I can't remember
what happened in the past.

64
00:05:34,590 --> 00:05:36,230
I only know my sacred title

65
00:05:36,230 --> 00:05:37,960
but can't recall where I came from

66
00:05:38,470 --> 00:05:40,030
or what happened before.

67
00:05:40,150 --> 00:05:40,990
Master,

68
00:05:41,030 --> 00:05:42,790
I have no grievance with you.

69
00:05:43,030 --> 00:05:45,120
Why must you enter my body?

70
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,440
Someone

71
00:05:47,470 --> 00:05:48,830
brought me to you.

72
00:05:48,910 --> 00:05:50,640
Because we are the same kind of people.

73
00:05:53,150 --> 00:05:55,520
Master, can you explain it more clearly?

74
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:58,080
I instinctively feel this way.

75
00:05:58,390 --> 00:05:59,440
I can't remember

76
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,270
more than that.

77
00:06:02,230 --> 00:06:04,560
Who brought you here, Master?

78
00:06:23,910 --> 00:06:24,750
Follow me.

79
00:06:33,340 --> 00:06:34,660
(Linyuan Pass)

80
00:06:34,660 --> 00:06:36,340
(High with Moat)

81
00:06:44,270 --> 00:06:45,470
That man in black

82
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:46,910
is the one who brought me here.

83
00:06:47,150 --> 00:06:48,710
I once merged with him

84
00:06:48,710 --> 00:06:51,270
and got this memory
from his primordial spirit.

85
00:06:52,350 --> 00:06:53,520
Who is that man in black?

86
00:06:55,590 --> 00:06:56,640
I don't know.

87
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:59,590
You merged with him

88
00:06:59,830 --> 00:07:01,880
like you did with Heng Hui.

89
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:05,350
(The Sangbo Case)

90
00:07:05,650 --> 00:07:07,620
(still has secrets behind it.)

91
00:07:08,230 --> 00:07:11,030
(Could it be to merge with this demon?)

92
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:12,640
I am not a demon.

93
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,440
I am called Shen Shu.

94
00:07:15,830 --> 00:07:17,640
How can you hear what I'm thinking?

95
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:19,200
I have merged with you.

96
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:21,760
I know what you're thinking.

97
00:07:22,470 --> 00:07:23,390
Nonsense.

98
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:27,280
Nine, eight.

99
00:07:32,470 --> 00:07:33,310
One, two.

100
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:36,520
Two, zero.

101
00:07:38,590 --> 00:07:41,390
3.14159265597.

102
00:07:41,390 --> 00:07:44,150
1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 4, 3, 2, 1.

103
00:07:44,150 --> 00:07:45,000
1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7.

104
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,080
Stop.

105
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:49,000
Don't worry.

106
00:07:49,640 --> 00:07:51,200
I won't harm you.

107
00:07:52,590 --> 00:07:53,430
Yes,

108
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:55,390
I need to stay in your body for a while.

109
00:07:55,390 --> 00:07:56,520
But your body

110
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,470
is much stronger than Heng Hui's.

111
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:01,560
I won't devour your energy
or kill the innocent.

112
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,680
I won't possess you

113
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:04,470
nor control you.

114
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:07,230
Fine, fine,

115
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,470
I get it.

116
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:11,080
You're like the worm in my stomach.

117
00:08:11,270 --> 00:08:13,440
You know everything I think.

118
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:14,470
In that case,

119
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:17,350
I'll stay here and recover.

120
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:19,680
Thank you, benefactor.

121
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,000
No, no, wait.

122
00:08:21,230 --> 00:08:23,590
Master, I'm just a humble Guardian.

123
00:08:23,590 --> 00:08:25,200
I can't help you with anything.

124
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:26,960
You might as well find another host.

125
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:27,830
No.

126
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:29,790
Your body

127
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:31,200
is very strong.

128
00:08:31,270 --> 00:08:33,750
I feel very comfortable in your body.

129
00:08:33,750 --> 00:08:36,110
Also, inside you, there is something

130
00:08:36,800 --> 00:08:38,510
that can help me nourish my severed arm.

131
00:08:39,470 --> 00:08:40,310
Something?

132
00:08:41,230 --> 00:08:42,110
What thing?

133
00:08:43,040 --> 00:08:44,960
I don't know.

134
00:08:45,680 --> 00:08:46,680
I only know

135
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:47,960
that thing

136
00:08:48,350 --> 00:08:50,040
was not originally inside you.

137
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,560
Someone deliberately

138
00:08:52,230 --> 00:08:53,680
put it there.

139
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:54,920
Well then.

140
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:57,080
Master, you can just
take that thing away.

141
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:59,510
- I absolutely won't...
- It's connected to you.

142
00:08:59,750 --> 00:09:01,400
I don't know its origin,

143
00:09:01,830 --> 00:09:03,350
and I can't take it away.

144
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:06,160
So, you're sticking to me now.

145
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:07,810
Besides using this place to recover,

146
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:09,280
there's one more thing

147
00:09:09,510 --> 00:09:10,590
I need to ask you for.

148
00:09:10,710 --> 00:09:12,110
Now you're going too far.

149
00:09:12,110 --> 00:09:13,400
Help me search for the past

150
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:14,450
and recover my memories.

151
00:09:14,800 --> 00:09:15,990
In the process,

152
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:18,710
I will give you some help.

153
00:09:19,870 --> 00:09:20,710
Help?

154
00:09:20,830 --> 00:09:22,560
There are few in this world

155
00:09:22,750 --> 00:09:23,710
who can defeat me.

156
00:09:23,890 --> 00:09:25,080
Those three Gold Gongs

157
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:27,300
and the sorcerer from the Bureau
were no match for me.

158
00:09:35,470 --> 00:09:36,710
As long as I'm here,

159
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:39,590
it's like you have an extra trump card.

160
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:44,510
A cheat.

161
00:09:45,830 --> 00:09:46,800
What cheat?

162
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:48,830
I am called Shen Shu.

163
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,320
Cheat Shen Shu.

164
00:09:50,750 --> 00:09:51,590
No.

165
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,680
Master Shen Shu.

166
00:09:53,280 --> 00:09:54,230
Master Shen Shu,

167
00:09:55,830 --> 00:09:57,110
from my observations,

168
00:09:57,110 --> 00:09:59,080
I now know some things

169
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,870
about your origin.

170
00:10:01,800 --> 00:10:02,640
What do you know?

171
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:04,710
You must be

172
00:10:05,510 --> 00:10:06,630
from Tianyu.

173
00:10:08,400 --> 00:10:09,350
How can you tell?

174
00:10:12,830 --> 00:10:13,680
Your demeanor.

175
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:19,680
I see.

176
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:22,440
So, I am from Tianyu.

177
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:23,560
Good, good.

178
00:10:23,560 --> 00:10:24,810
I'll rely on you in the future.

179
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:26,750
Please take care of me.

180
00:10:26,750 --> 00:10:27,680
Of course.

181
00:10:51,860 --> 00:10:55,500
(Tianyu)

182
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:03,110
The soup base from the Dafeng

183
00:11:03,680 --> 00:11:06,350
is way better than our Tianyu's.

184
00:11:06,350 --> 00:11:07,190
Come on.

185
00:11:09,510 --> 00:11:10,350
Bro,

186
00:11:10,590 --> 00:11:11,830
we're lucky today.

187
00:11:12,110 --> 00:11:13,320
With that wild rabbit,

188
00:11:13,830 --> 00:11:14,990
plus a marten,

189
00:11:14,990 --> 00:11:16,190
it's enough to make a fur coat

190
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:17,320
for our younger brother.

191
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:18,380
I'll go up the mountain

192
00:11:18,450 --> 00:11:19,830
and catch a snow deer

193
00:11:20,110 --> 00:11:21,160
to make you one

194
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:22,040
for the winter.

195
00:11:22,560 --> 00:11:23,400
Stop.

196
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:26,040
Where are your parents?

197
00:11:26,470 --> 00:11:27,400
I don't know.

198
00:11:28,630 --> 00:11:29,750
Don't know?

199
00:11:40,470 --> 00:11:41,350
It's a hallucination.

200
00:11:45,710 --> 00:11:46,830
Without this,

201
00:11:47,350 --> 00:11:50,440
how could I see the true form
of Tianyu Dharma?

202
00:11:52,470 --> 00:11:53,590
Reveal yourself.

203
00:11:57,710 --> 00:11:58,390
Who are you?

204
00:11:58,400 --> 00:12:00,580
(Du'e, Tianyu Prophet, 3rd Rank Vajra)
Why disturb us?

205
00:12:00,580 --> 00:12:02,730
(Duku, Tianyu Prophet, 2nd Rank Arhat)
A Hypnotizer.

206
00:12:02,940 --> 00:12:05,080
(3rd Rank Hypnotizer
from the Witcher's Sect)

207
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:06,470
Greetings, Prophets.

208
00:12:06,680 --> 00:12:08,440
Sorry for my rudeness.

209
00:12:08,890 --> 00:12:11,920
I came to deliver a message.

210
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,160
Shen Shu

211
00:12:13,470 --> 00:12:14,590
has emerged.

212
00:12:25,380 --> 00:12:27,820
(Xu Mansion)

213
00:12:30,280 --> 00:12:31,440
(What to do?)

214
00:12:32,510 --> 00:12:33,630
(Should I)

215
00:12:33,710 --> 00:12:35,750
(report this?)

216
00:12:46,130 --> 00:12:47,600
(Guardian, Lord Wei)
As a Guardian,

217
00:12:47,680 --> 00:12:49,280
you only need to stick to your duty.

218
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:51,400
Remember.

219
00:12:51,990 --> 00:12:53,200
Even if the sky falls,

220
00:12:53,560 --> 00:12:54,800
I will protect you.

221
00:12:55,680 --> 00:12:58,110
(Lord Wei surely values me.)

222
00:12:58,830 --> 00:13:01,630
(If he can remove
this severed hand from me,)

223
00:13:02,280 --> 00:13:03,710
(then it's not a problem.)

224
00:13:04,760 --> 00:13:06,000
(But if he can't...)

225
00:13:07,110 --> 00:13:10,030
(Sangbo Lake, demonic hand, explosion)
(It's from the Sangbo lakebed.)

226
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,800
(Will he cover for me)

227
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:14,320
(or seal me along with it?)

228
00:13:24,780 --> 00:13:26,500
(Tell the Supervisor)
The Supervisor...

229
00:13:27,510 --> 00:13:28,810
(With his abilities,)

230
00:13:29,510 --> 00:13:31,670
(he's surely able
to remove the severed hand.)

231
00:13:33,710 --> 00:13:35,040
(But he's too mysterious.)

232
00:13:35,590 --> 00:13:37,510
(Though I've never met him,)

233
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:39,990
(he seems to have always been
watching me.)

234
00:13:40,870 --> 00:13:42,050
(Will he help me?)

235
00:13:47,380 --> 00:13:50,420
(Tell the Supervisor)

236
00:13:51,300 --> 00:13:53,160
(That Hypnotizer)

237
00:13:53,680 --> 00:13:56,530
(used great effort to release the seal.)

238
00:13:59,110 --> 00:14:01,040
(Why did it end up in my body?)

239
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:07,350
(Who is he?)

240
00:14:08,130 --> 00:14:09,510
(What's his real purpose?)

241
00:14:11,560 --> 00:14:13,650
(Will he take the severed hand back?)

242
00:14:16,380 --> 00:14:17,760
(For now,)

243
00:14:18,050 --> 00:14:20,450
(I need to find out his identity asap.)

244
00:14:21,830 --> 00:14:23,680
(Well, the problem is back.)

245
00:14:24,040 --> 00:14:25,680
(How should I figure it out?)

246
00:14:26,590 --> 00:14:28,470
(Should I seek help from others?)

247
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:31,040
Keep the secret.

248
00:14:39,590 --> 00:14:40,830
Master?

249
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:43,470
You're here?

250
00:14:47,920 --> 00:14:48,760
Master,

251
00:14:49,510 --> 00:14:51,160
do you have more clues about that man?

252
00:14:51,160 --> 00:14:52,510
Tell me more.

253
00:14:53,920 --> 00:14:54,760
Master,

254
00:14:56,830 --> 00:14:59,680
you said we were
the same kind of people.

255
00:14:59,990 --> 00:15:01,510
What does that mean?

256
00:15:01,750 --> 00:15:03,630
Do you also pick up silver every day?

257
00:15:04,040 --> 00:15:06,990
Or are you good at pitch-pot?

258
00:15:07,350 --> 00:15:08,190
Ring toss?

259
00:15:08,190 --> 00:15:09,110
Do you never miss it?

260
00:15:10,830 --> 00:15:12,470
Master, say something.

261
00:15:12,680 --> 00:15:14,230
Why not come out for a chat?

262
00:15:14,350 --> 00:15:15,800
I'll make you a cup of milk tea.

263
00:15:17,470 --> 00:15:18,400
Come on, Master.

264
00:15:19,470 --> 00:15:20,310
Master.

265
00:15:20,350 --> 00:15:21,190
Master.

266
00:15:21,230 --> 00:15:22,680
Master, Master.

267
00:15:22,800 --> 00:15:24,800
Master, say something.

268
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:26,280
Why just those three words?

269
00:15:26,280 --> 00:15:27,470
Master.

270
00:15:27,870 --> 00:15:28,710
Master.

271
00:15:29,590 --> 00:15:30,510
Master.

272
00:15:30,860 --> 00:15:33,620
(Haoqi Tower)

273
00:15:38,320 --> 00:15:39,400
Greetings, Lord Wei.

274
00:15:41,080 --> 00:15:41,920
You're here.

275
00:15:43,230 --> 00:15:44,070
Lord Wei,

276
00:15:44,630 --> 00:15:47,590
I heard that His Majesty
was upset at the Bureau

277
00:15:47,630 --> 00:15:49,230
after knowing I took the Elixir of Life.

278
00:15:49,630 --> 00:15:51,360
His Majesty's asked for it
for three years,

279
00:15:51,590 --> 00:15:53,030
but the Supervisor didn't give him.

280
00:15:54,110 --> 00:15:54,960
Now,

281
00:15:55,350 --> 00:15:57,080
you must keep a low profile

282
00:15:57,560 --> 00:15:58,870
and conceal your talent.

283
00:16:02,990 --> 00:16:04,830
Make good use of the Elixir of Life.

