694
00:37:50,550 --> 00:37:51,720
What else did you tell him?

695
00:37:52,280 --> 00:37:54,070
Just a little.

696
00:37:54,400 --> 00:37:56,070
How much did you tell him?

697
00:37:57,110 --> 00:37:58,920
Just a little.

698
00:37:58,920 --> 00:38:00,240
I didn't say much.

699
00:38:00,320 --> 00:38:03,150
Just your identity, age, cultivation,

700
00:38:03,150 --> 00:38:04,280
your worldly experience,

701
00:38:04,840 --> 00:38:06,150
and your crush on your senior.

702
00:38:11,590 --> 00:38:12,440
I'm warning you.

703
00:38:12,800 --> 00:38:14,630
Don't tell No. 3 anything about me.

704
00:38:14,760 --> 00:38:17,650
If there is even the slightest leak,
I'll guarantee your tragic death.

705
00:38:19,030 --> 00:38:20,190
Xinnian told me

706
00:38:20,320 --> 00:38:22,360
